 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。

2005年6月，森美·李爾回到曾經效力的[[保頓足球會|保頓]]擔任助理領隊，協助領隊[[艾拿戴斯|艾拿戴斯]]。2006年8月，[[英格蘭足球總會|足總]]欲委任森美·李爾擔任[[英格蘭U21|英格蘭U21]]的領隊，但他拒絕，並離任成年國家隊的教練職務
<ref>{{cite news|title=Lee leaves England coaching team|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/5255978.stm|publisher=BBC新聞|date=2006-08-08|accessdate=2007-04-30|archive-date=2006-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060826144351/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/5255978.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

艾拿戴斯在2007年4月離任保頓領隊，森美·李爾證實接任領隊<ref name="bwfc">{{cite web|title=Club statement |url=http://www.bwfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/General/0,,1004~1145252,00.html |publisher=[[保頓足球會|保頓足球會]]官方網頁 |date=2007-10-17 |accessdate=2007-10-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120730064916/http://www.bwfc.co.uk/page/General/0%2C%2C1004~1145252%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-07-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lee appointed manager of Bolton|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6606553.stm|publisher=BBC新聞|date=2007-04-30|accessdate=2007-04-30|archive-date=2008-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080403024120/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bolton_wanderers/6606553.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他執教的11場聯賽中僅勝一場，結果在2007年10月被解僱，成為該賽季第二位被解僱的領隊<ref name="bwfc"/>。

在森美·李爾和[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]領隊[[賓尼迪斯|賓尼迪斯]]一起看利物浦預備組的比賽後，有傳言指森美·李爾將回歸利物浦擔任[[賓尼迪斯|賓尼迪斯]]的副手<ref>{{cite news|title=Rafa Benitez and Sammy Lee's old pals' act|url=http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/0100news/tm_headline=rafa-benitez-and-sammy-lee-s-old-pals-act&method=full&objectid=20106790&siteid=50061-name_page.html|publisher=icLiverpool|date=2007-11-14|accessdate=2008-01-08|archive-date=2011-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516182109/http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0500liverpoolfc/0100news/tm_headline%3Drafa-benitez-and-sammy-lee-s-old-pals-act%26method%3Dfull%26objectid%3D20106790%26siteid%3D50061-name_page.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亦傳言指[[列斯聯|列斯聯]]的領隊[[麥亞里士打|麥亞里士打]]有意邀請森美·李爾擔任助理領隊<ref>{{cite news|title=Leeds United number two: decision due|url=http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-number-two-decision.3734782.jp|publisher=Yorkshire Evening Post|date=2008-02-01|accessdate=2008-02-22|archive-date=2009-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090102235243/http://www.yorkshireeveningpost.co.uk/leedsunited/Leeds-United-number-two-decision.3734782.jp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2008年5月16日，因[[利物浦足球俱樂部|利物浦]]的教練{{tsl|en|Alex Miller|阿歷斯·米拿}}（Alex Miller）離任前往[[日本職業足球聯賽|日本]]執教[[JEF聯市原·千葉|JEF聯市原·千葉]]，森美·李爾正式回歸利物浦擔任[[賓尼迪斯|賓尼迪斯]]的副手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.teamtalk.com/football/story/0,16368,1776_3542158,00.html|title=Lee lined up as Rafa's assistant|publisher=Teamtalk|date=2008-05-09|accessdate=2008-05-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803043504/http://www.teamtalk.com/football/story/0,16368,1776_3542158,00.html|archivedate=2008-08-03}}</ref>，與利物浦簽訂兩年合約，擔任紅軍的助理領隊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/7401046.stm|title=Lee clinches return to Liverpool|publisher=BBC|date=2008-05-16|accessdate=2008-05-16|archive-date=2008-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080518025719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/7401046.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N159939080516-1155.htm|title=Benítez welcomes Lee addition|publisher=利物浦足球俱樂部官方網頁|date=2008-05-16|accessdate=2008-05-16|archive-date=2008-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080518082233/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N159939080516-1155.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年12月21日對[[阿仙奴|阿仙奴]]的[[英超|英超]]聯賽，森美·李爾暫代患上[[腎結石|腎結石]]的領隊[[賓尼迪斯|賓尼迪斯]]領軍，最終在客場[[酋长球场|酋长球场]]打成1-1<ref>{{cite web|url=http://soccer.titan24.com/08-12-22/153848.html|title=副帅越俎代庖抢回1分 萨米：贝帅该为电话费烦了|publisher=体坛网|date=2008-12-22|accessdate=2009-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429090439/http://soccer.titan24.com/08-12-22/153848.html|archive-date=2011-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

